{
 "name": "RPlog_Preparation_of_the_Jedi",
 "title": "Preparation of the Jedi",
 "summary": "On the bridge of the NRCV Audacity, Luke Skywalker confers with the Sullustan Jedi Enb'Zik and the pilot Rook about the gathering crisis over Dac and Caspar. Grimly weighing the possibility that the Sith Tyler now commands a criminal organization -- giving the galaxy's enemies two bases of power -- the three agree the looming confrontation is inevitable. They settle on their goals: break the Imperial blockade, evacuate their people, and extract Tyler from the area. Clearing their minds and steeling themselves, the Jedi and their allies prepare for the difficult work ahead.",
